App structure:

0. Users
    1 Admin (Grace)
        login, password, and logged in state handled by restful_authentication
    Many viewers
    Each controller has edit and update actions for the admin, as well as a show action for the viewers

1. Information side
    Bio Controller
        no index, new, create, or delete methods
    
    Bio / Account / Admin User
        * restful_authentication fields *
        picture
        description
        facts
        resume ?
        
    Contact Controller
        no show method
        
    Contact
        method
        link
        icon
    
    Feedback
        name
        email
        feedback
    
2. Gallery side
    Galleries Controller
        presents a gallery full of 1 or more categories
    
    Gallery
        name
        + categories
    Category
        name
        order
        _ gallery_id
        + artworks
    Artwork
        image_file_name
        image_content_type
        image_file_size
        title
        description
        order
        _ category_id
        + details
    Detail
        file
        _ artwork_id
    